  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/071840fe5987f2e61992e449dc1ec253.poster.avif?t=1773473273\" width=600 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/071840fe5987f2e61992e449dc1ec253.webm?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/071840fe5987f2e61992e449dc1ec253.mp4?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for Frenzied War!<br><strong>Pure adrenaline! Deadzone Blackout is a frantic FPS that throws you into chaotic, fast-paced combat.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master the Fast-Paced Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/fbe5ec431854715fca5f6c34c7d40284.poster.avif?t=1773473273\" width=624 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/fbe5ec431854715fca5f6c34c7d40284.webm?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/fbe5ec431854715fca5f6c34c7d40284.mp4?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>Fluid and intuitive movement: Slide, jump and crouch with complete freedom to dodge your enemies and flank their positions.</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sharp and deadly shots: Aim precisely and eliminate your opponents with a variety of customizable weapons. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Brutal hand-to-hand combat: Use knives, grenades to eliminate your enemies in visceral combat.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your class and customize your playstyle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/8b789e98cd7cba9e68f0d1babf87eac2.poster.avif?t=1773473273\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/8b789e98cd7cba9e68f0d1babf87eac2.webm?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/8b789e98cd7cba9e68f0d1babf87eac2.mp4?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>Assault: Versatile soldier with a focus on hand-to-hand combat and assault weapons.</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>Engineer: Specialist in explosives and team support with grenade launchers and shields.</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Support: Provide healing and ammo to your allies with medkits and ammo crates. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recon: Dominate the battlefield with vision and reconnaissance using drones and sniper rifles. </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience the fury of combat in 3 game modes</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/13ffa05c6e1e8bd8a64ca456a7c1ecd0.poster.avif?t=1773473273\" width=624 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/13ffa05c6e1e8bd8a64ca456a7c1ecd0.webm?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/13ffa05c6e1e8bd8a64ca456a7c1ecd0.mp4?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>Team Deathmatch: Show your strength and eliminate the opposing team in a bloody battle.</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free For All: Save yourself if you can! Be the last survivor in chaotic and relentless combat. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Capture the Flag: Coordinate with your allies and capture the enemy flag in a race against time. </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deadzone Blackout offers:</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/f2d7d2947a244a6dc4e8e6d832009ea5.poster.avif?t=1773473273\" width=624 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/f2d7d2947a244a6dc4e8e6d832009ea5.webm?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/f2d7d2947a244a6dc4e8e6d832009ea5.mp4?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>Competitive ranking system: Fight to reach the top of the rankings and prove that you are the best player.</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>Private and public matches: Play with friends or players from around the world.</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Regular Events and Challenges: Participate in exciting events and earn exclusive rewards. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mod support and customization: Customize your game with mods and create your own experience. </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deadzone Blackout: Adrenaline runs through your veins! </strong><br><strong>Prepare for war!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/203db85f3dd92e2c3f4f74d0945e20ea.poster.avif?t=1773473273\" width=624 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/203db85f3dd92e2c3f4f74d0945e20ea.webm?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915590/extras/203db85f3dd92e2c3f4f74d0945e20ea.mp4?t=1773473273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In the final version, this game will include optional purchases of virtual currency to acquire virtual items.</strong></p>",
